@node "General info" "General information"

Filename : RSAD " Remote Sysop Access Door "
Version  : 3.01
Author   : Ashly Braggins
Function : Allows Remote Sysop's to perform functions from a door,
           Thus Cutting down on seperate menus...

This door should work with versions 1.52-54 of MAX'sBBS, Untested to see
if it works on any other version of MAXsBBS...

Compiled with HisoftBASIC version 1.05 and requires the HisoftBasic.library

  Special thanks to Randy Quick for his insight into password camouflage
  and also for allowing me to incorperate his User and Files Editors into
  the Program...

Also Included with this archive is a Door called FakeRSAD, For more
information on this door, see Installing RSAD 3.01

@endnode
